description: Lists all approval rule templates in the specified Amazon Web Services Region in your Amazon Web Services account. If an Amazon Web Services Region is not specified, the Amazon Web Services Region where you are signed in is used.

nested_items.name: approvalRuleTemplateNames
nested_items.description: The names of all the approval rule templates found in the Amazon Web Services Region for your Amazon Web Services account.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: An enumeration token that allows the operation to batch the next results of the operation.
